This glowing, indestructible crystal looks a little out of place here. There is a symbol of an open book etched near the bottom - likely a hallmark of some kind. Apparently placed by a mage of great power, this crystal takes magical energy and uses it stabilize the positive energy rifts for just a moment. This seems to come with the side effect of drawing the attention of a very large elemental.

// Activated by using Greater Mythal on it. Once enough have been used, it will activate the boss fight. Only one mythal may be used per character. Be warned: This is dangerous!

Value.value: *The device trembles and released a strong burst of positive energy! Soon a massive elemental stomps towards you and your group, clearly drawn by the magic of the crystal!*
*This crystal  doesn't seem to function when an elemental is nearby, or when the exit crystal's energy hasn't been spent.*
The blinding light and positive energy from the plane begin to overwhelm you
